<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 14:07:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列科学家发现焦虑与低睾酮水平之间缺失联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-scientists-discover-missing-link-between-anxiety-and-low-testosterone/0000018d-40b2-d02c-a79f-43bb44b50000</link><description>众所周知，雄性激素缺乏与焦虑有关，现在我们知道了其中的原因。如果你的老鼠患有麻痹性焦虑症，注射一针睾酮可能会给他带来奇迹，但在未来，这一发现提出了一种新方法</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 13:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-scientists-discover-missing-link-between-anxiety-and-low-testosterone/0000018d-40b2-d02c-a79f-43bb44b50000</guid></item><item><title>先是拜登，现在是卡塔尔：内塔尼亚胡正在创造敌人，以使他的中东永远战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/first-biden-now-qatar-netanyahu-is-creating-nemeses-to-get-his-mideast-forever-war/0000018d-4061-d02c-a79f-43fb9cc20000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡称卡塔尔代表以色列人质的调解角色“有问题”，这将他的战时行为推向了新的低点——这对一个不理解“公共礼仪”或“接受责任”等术语的人来说是有道理的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 13:29:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/first-biden-now-qatar-netanyahu-is-creating-nemeses-to-get-his-mideast-forever-war/0000018d-4061-d02c-a79f-43fb9cc20000</guid></item><item><title>柏林展览聚焦加沙最年轻的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/berlin-exhibit-spotlights-youngest-hostage-held-in-gaza/0000018d-40a2-dc44-a5bf-c8b6be5f0000</link><description>为了纪念 Kfir Bibas 的一周岁生日，柏林举办了一场展览，汇集了献给与家人一起被绑架到加沙的红发男婴的作品</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 13:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/berlin-exhibit-spotlights-youngest-hostage-held-in-gaza/0000018d-40a2-dc44-a5bf-c8b6be5f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列为拯救约旦河西岸迈出一小步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-takes-one-small-step-to-rescue-the-west-bank/0000018d-407c-d02c-a79f-43ff487b0000</link><description>以色列周日批准向巴勒斯坦权力机构提供资金的计划是一个良好的开端，但不足以使西岸免遭经济破坏</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 12:09:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-takes-one-small-step-to-rescue-the-west-bank/0000018d-407c-d02c-a79f-43ff487b0000</guid></item><item><title>只有巴解组织脱离哈马斯，才会有巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/therell-only-be-a-palestinian-state-if-the-plo-disengages-from-hamas/0000018d-3fa7-d35c-a39f-bfff192c0000</link><description>巴解组织准备承认对整个巴勒斯坦的“历史性权利”，包括难民返回的权利。另一方面，哈马斯坚持继续对以色列进行武装斗争</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 11:53:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/therell-only-be-a-palestinian-state-if-the-plo-disengages-from-hamas/0000018d-3fa7-d35c-a39f-bfff192c0000</guid></item><item><title>在你的右边，是一个屠杀现场：10 月 7 日的暴行，游客涌入以色列南部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-your-right-a-massacre-site-oct-7-atrocities-tourists-are-inundating-southern-israel/0000018d-3b8c-d35c-a39f-bbdeb1de0000</link><description>除了团结和纪念之外，一些人担心加沙边境社区将成为博物馆，纪念活动将掩盖大屠杀的痕迹，而且这些地点将被荒唐地商业化</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 11:52:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-your-right-a-massacre-site-oct-7-atrocities-tourists-are-inundating-southern-israel/0000018d-3b8c-d35c-a39f-bbdeb1de0000</guid></item><item><title>回到加沙边境失落的 70 年代以色列嬉皮士天堂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/books/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/back-to-the-70s-hippie-haven-on-the-gaza-border/0000018d-3b24-d3a5-afdf-7f37f5190000</link><description>凯雷姆沙洛姆基布兹是左翼抗议和狂欢狂欢的温床。 Avihu Ronen 教授刚刚出版了一本书，回顾了他在那里的 11 年，并解释了为什么基布兹的精神在今天比以往任何时候都更加重要</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 11:12:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/books/2024-01-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/back-to-the-70s-hippie-haven-on-the-gaza-border/0000018d-3b24-d3a5-afdf-7f37f5190000</guid></item><item><title>法国告诉以色列，反对建立加沙边境缓冲区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/france-tells-israel-it-opposes-creation-of-gaza-border-buffer-zone/0000018d-3fa3-dc44-a5bf-bfb74d820000</link><description>在国防部长访问之后，法国官方消息人士称，该安全区旨在阻止恐怖分子渗透到以色列，这将使巴勒斯坦权力机构难以控制加沙</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:52:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/france-tells-israel-it-opposes-creation-of-gaza-border-buffer-zone/0000018d-3fa3-dc44-a5bf-bfb74d820000</guid></item><item><title>兼顾军事义务和财产法：以色列国防军预备役学生努力跟上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/juggling-military-duty-and-property-law-students-in-reserves-struggle-to-keep-up/0000018d-3cdc-d02c-a79f-7fdfbe900000</link><description>随着以色列学年的开始，大学试图帮助从战争中退伍的学生补上他们错过的材料。然而，并不是每个人都能参加，有些参加的人也很难集中注意力。一位讲师表示：“显然他们正在付出代价”</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 04:01:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/juggling-military-duty-and-property-law-students-in-reserves-struggle-to-keep-up/0000018d-3cdc-d02c-a79f-7fdfbe900000</guid></item><item><title>尽管不符合标准，以色列极右翼部长秘书仍获得持枪许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/secretary-of-far-right-israeli-minister-gets-gun-permit-despite-not-meeting-criteria/0000018d-3d30-d02c-a79f-7fbbf7cb0000</link><description>为尼利·卡多什颁发执照的高级军官奥菲尔·布基 (Ofir Buki) 在签署请求几天后就晋升为指挥官</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 04:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/secretary-of-far-right-israeli-minister-gets-gun-permit-despite-not-meeting-criteria/0000018d-3d30-d02c-a79f-7fbbf7cb0000</guid></item><item><title>两架无人机越过黎巴嫩边境进入以色列；加沙边境火箭警报响起</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-live/qatar-harshly-rebukes-netanyahu-for-allegedly-labeling-it-as-problematic/0000018d-3e9c-d02c-a79f-7f9f6f250000</link><description>在黎巴嫩边境附近发现可疑人员的报告后，以色列国防军表示对该地区的扫描没有发现渗透的迹象 ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告以色列军队与杰宁当地武装部队之间发生武装冲突 ■ 以色列国防军正在调查近东救济工程处的袭击，称不是由于以色列国防军空袭或炮火造成的 ■ 国际法院将于周五发布裁决，南非外交部长预计将出席听证会 ■ 以色列消息人士称双方远未就新的人质协议达成一致 ■ 美国军方证实胡塞武装向悬挂美国国旗的船只开火</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 03:21:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article-live/qatar-harshly-rebukes-netanyahu-for-allegedly-labeling-it-as-problematic/0000018d-3e9c-d02c-a79f-7f9f6f250000</guid></item><item><title>艾哈迈德·阿布·拉蒂夫喜欢“将不同文化融合在一起”。他在葬礼上又做了一次</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/ahmad-abu-latif-loved-to-bring-cultures-together-he-did-it-again-at-his-funeral/0000018d-3d35-d02c-a79f-7fbf38c10000</link><description>尽管下着雨，而且几乎一片漆黑，数百人——犹太人和阿拉伯人、宗教人士和世俗人士、年轻人和老年人——聚集在一起参加中士的葬礼。一等兵（后）艾哈迈德·阿布·拉蒂夫，自愿参加战斗并于周一在加沙地带被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 01:33:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/ahmad-abu-latif-loved-to-bring-cultures-together-he-did-it-again-at-his-funeral/0000018d-3d35-d02c-a79f-7fbf38c10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陆军参谋长反击监察机构调查，凸显与内塔尼亚胡的紧张关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-chief-pushes-back-against-watchdog-probe-highlighting-tension-with-netanyahu/0000018d-3d38-d35c-a39f-bf7a03fe0000</link><description>哈莱维表示，国家审计长计划在战争仍在进行时调查以色列国防军的行为，这是史无前例的，这将阻止军队实现其目标</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 00:34:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-chief-pushes-back-against-watchdog-probe-highlighting-tension-with-netanyahu/0000018d-3d38-d35c-a39f-bf7a03fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列代理监狱管理局局长的第一步：巴勒斯坦恐怖分子面临更严酷的条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/acting-prison-service-chiefs-first-steps-harsher-conditions-for-palestinian-terrorists/0000018d-3d1c-d02c-a79f-7f9f17a50000</link><description>新任命的监狱长科比·雅科比 (Kobi Ya&amp;#39;akobi) 誓言要对恐怖分子囚犯实行更严厉的监狱条件，但此前曾谈到改善犹太恐怖分子嫌疑人的条件。作为伊塔马尔·本·格维尔 (Itamar Ben Gvir) 的私人朋友，雅科比将“遵守极右翼部长的政策”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 22:33:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-25/ty-article/.premium/acting-prison-service-chiefs-first-steps-harsher-conditions-for-palestinian-terrorists/0000018d-3d1c-d02c-a79f-7f9f17a50000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔严厉斥责内塔尼亚胡涉嫌将其标记为“有问题”：可能会破坏加沙的调解努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/qatar-harshly-rebukes-netanyahu-for-allegedly-labeling-it-as-problematic/0000018d-3d27-d35c-a39f-bf7f63970000</link><description>以色列总理批评多哈角色的录音曝光后，卡塔尔外交部发言人指责内塔尼亚胡“出于政治原因”故意阻碍调解努力</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 21:13:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/qatar-harshly-rebukes-netanyahu-for-allegedly-labeling-it-as-problematic/0000018d-3d27-d35c-a39f-bf7f63970000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院周五就以色列种族灭绝案中的加沙紧急措施做出裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/icj-to-rule-on-gaza-emergency-measures-in-israel-genocide-case-on-friday/0000018d-3d12-dc44-a5bf-bdb684e80000</link><description>在即将到来的裁决中，法院不会处理以色列是否在加沙实施国家主导的种族灭绝的主要问题，而只会决定是否发布紧急命令，以防止争端进一步恶化，同时法院继续调查完整案例</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 20:21:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/icj-to-rule-on-gaza-emergency-measures-in-israel-genocide-case-on-friday/0000018d-3d12-dc44-a5bf-bdb684e80000</guid></item><item><title>“你在为哈马斯火上浇油！”：那么，什么时候是为人质而战的最佳时机呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-24/ty-article/.highlight/the-eradication-of-hamas-will-take-time-the-hostages-dont-have/0000018d-3c53-d02c-a79f-7fdbe1f50000</link><description>当以色列妇女面临以色列人的尖刻批评时，他们称她们的抗议活动是在“助长哈马斯”，要求达成协议释放加沙的俘虏，我们必须问：那么，什么时候为释放人质而奋斗合适呢？</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 18:54:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-24/ty-article/.highlight/the-eradication-of-hamas-will-take-time-the-hostages-dont-have/0000018d-3c53-d02c-a79f-7fdbe1f50000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装对以色列和西方的袭击使也门名声大噪——但也门人的情况又如何呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/houthi-attacks-on-israel-put-yemen-on-the-map-but-what-is-it-like-for-yemenis/0000018d-367e-d58f-a3af-b77efd440000</link><description>也门长达十年的内战对这个拥有 3300 万人口的本已贫困的国家造成了毁灭性影响，胡塞运动造成长期水和食物短缺、疫苗武器化和虐待儿童</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 17:27:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/houthi-attacks-on-israel-put-yemen-on-the-map-but-what-is-it-like-for-yemenis/0000018d-367e-d58f-a3af-b77efd440000</guid></item><item><title>数十名以色列国防军女性观察员新兵在分配后拒绝在部队服役</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/dozens-of-female-idf-spotter-recruits-refuse-to-serve-in-unit-after-assignment/0000018d-3c26-d07d-a79d-fde7dbf60000</link><description>大约 50 名女性新兵被选为观察员，该部队于 10 月 7 日遭到袭击，其士兵在加沙仍被扣为人质，她们显然拒绝接受该部队的任务</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 17:08:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/dozens-of-female-idf-spotter-recruits-refuse-to-serve-in-unit-after-assignment/0000018d-3c26-d07d-a79d-fde7dbf60000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯火箭弹杀死 21 名以色列士兵：加沙制造的串联弹头</title><link>ht